(1)

Henry Hudson Parkway, north from West 238th Street, showing it under construction. The bridge spans the Parkway at West 239th Street. Also shown (right), among the trees, is the war memorial to the World War veterans of this area.

May 25, 1937.

P. L. Sperr.

(2)

The same, another view.

P. L. Sperr.
